  "_comment": "Declarative team + functional-role configuration. Read by tools/route.py (deterministic routing) and the skills in .claude/commands/. Teams are curated subsets of the roster (bench vs council: 3-6 non-redundant voices beat headcount). Members reference roster.json slugs; roles reference the 'roles' registry below. Only status:active clones actually take a seat — others are reported as reserved. conditional_members: tag -> members added when the task classification carries that tag. review lists who checks the output; validate.py enforces that at least one review seat is NOT a default member (independent review).",
